Neither of these spells is rlly ideal for most lvl 65 wiz set ups.  <br>
<br>
The only way i've gotten to make super use of this spell is with focus effect: chill of umbra (26% to CR nukes) and ancient: destruction of ice.  this combonation (umbra, ice flame, destruction of ice) is EXTREMELY efficient, low aggro, and high dps.  only problem is that destruction of ice isn't spell most ppl have.<br>
<br>
other than that combonation i would prob use agnars or strike of solusok, or even just draught of eci with mage bracer over iceflame and any other &lt;60 spell.<br>
