With horse manarobe 2x harvest 355int etc I never run out of mana fighting in pop. SoS averages 3k damage per cast, it allows you to do more damage, gaining greater benefit from focus, and with ro/tash it's almost never resisted. Same can be said about agnarr, with tash and/or malo. Draughts with -50 resist is the standard nuke of choice in PoP for average wizards - no resist and low aggro.  Icespear gets partial and resisted often, iceflame adds very random damage. 1500 average is a stretch. <br>
<br>
