<br>
I have only seen one person include Mana Preservation in teh calculations, and that was since they use SoS. MP items are an essential part of any wizards gear as is getting SCM 1,2, and 3. Personally I use Iceflame on any raid, where I might end up needing a cold nuke.<br>
<br>
Iceflame also rocks for that big bang AE when using Winds of Gelid, however that does not make it a viable AE spell, even for for the most uber wizards.  Very long recycle time plus a huge mana drain even with MP gear and AA points.  IT is very situational.<br>
<br>
Most of the time I use SoS and Agnarr's plus 2 pop droughts, and maybe telekin.  I do not even have a lvl 60 nuke memmed.  However I do keep the buff up if for whatever reason I suddenly find myself needing a cold nuke.<br>
<br>
If it is a choice between the two...then agnarr's all the way.<br>
